node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Saint Hoax on September 14, 2021 tagging @nikkietutorials, and @theaffinitymag. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'AF Affinity Magazine @TheAffinityMag Nikkie de Jager pays tribute to Marsha P. Johnson at the #MetGala The "P" in Marsha' s name famously stood for "Pay It No Mind," which is printed on Nikki' s dress. Nikki aptly fits this year's gala theme by honoring an American icon who pioneered LGBTQ+ rights.'.

Kelly on one of the most anticipated albums of the year. Just tell us you don't care about Black girls + women, QUICKLY and GO! I'm so tired of BW & girls having to overlook & give up so much of ourselves to be apart of a culture we helped build.'.
Photo by Saint Hoax on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo shared by Saint Hoax on September 04, 2021 tagging @m.4rs. May be an image of text that says 'King Mars @_M4RS Drake literally put R Kelly on his album and y'all just eating it up. Y'all really cap. It's "protect black women" until one of y'all favorite artist drop a project feat the abuser suddenly y'all make exceptions.'.

Photo by Saint Hoax on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'justyna @justynaroz_ drake sampling r.kelly and kanye featuring marilyn manson and da baby really shows you men don't care about women and their trauma huh'.
